Risk Disclosure & Regulatory Notice


Trading leveraged products such as Forex, CFDs, and cryptocurrencies carries a high level of risk and may not be suitable for all investors. You should carefully consider your objectives, level of experience, and risk appetite before engaging in any trading activity. There is a possibility that you may sustain a loss equal to or greater than your entire investment. Therefore, you should not invest more than you can afford to lose. JC Securities Ltd. strictly adheres to international KYC (Know Your Customer) and AML (Anti-Money Laundering) regulations. All clients must undergo identity verification and risk assessment procedures prior to opening a trading account.


We do not offer or solicit services to residents or citizens of sanctioned jurisdictions, including but not limited to North Korea, Iran, Syria, Sudan, or to individuals and entities listed on any financial sanctions lists.
